Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.54,0:53:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were drenched in sweat when our eyes met,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.00,0:53:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,shining brighter than anyone else in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.38,0:53:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what the feeling was,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was ready for a new journey with you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.18,0:53:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget the breeze \Nas I watched you after the rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.53,0:53:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll shine bright enough to keep you warm
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.95,0:53:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to write the longest love story with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.37,0:53:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,coloring each page with our emotions, day after day
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.75,0:53:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like two stars lining up on a horoscope's page,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.19,0:54:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop wishing \Nour futures would intertwine
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart, covered in old scars,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.27,0:54:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is finally starting to heal
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.00,0:54:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love for it \Nwill make it beat like never before
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.52,0:54:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.36,0:54:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the emptiness in my heart started to disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.24,0:54:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly being filled \Nwith fleeting moments I had with you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.11,0:54:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look into your beautiful eyes forever
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.25,0:54:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and smile as you share \Nyour most intimate dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about how much \NI want to be your knight in shining armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.81,0:55:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it gives me all the courage \Nto take a step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.23,0:55:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I met you, \NI was always afraid of getting hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.60,0:55:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,always choosing to take the long way around
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.83,0:55:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My tough exterior has nowhere to go anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.34,0:55:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by the emotions I feel \Nwhen I'm around you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.67,0:55:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, when I learend of your true feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.13,0:55:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,my overflowing tears \Nsaid more than any words could
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.06,0:55:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if our paths won't always \Nhave the same road ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.03,0:55:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm determined to walk with you side by side
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.96,0:55:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a blank canvas \Nand paint it in our dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.49,0:55:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been searching for an excuse \Nto show you how I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.55,0:56:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the melody \Nof our love to stop playing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.93,0:56:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As I hold back my tears,\N fearing what your answer will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.31,0:56:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you this question, made of simple words,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.10,0:56:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This bond will last forever, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.03,0:56:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings for you are like raindrops \Nin the midnight clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.95,0:56:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,with nothing to stop them \Nfrom pouring down on you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.83,0:56:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my thoughts could catch up,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.50,0:56:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the wind after the rain had already come
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.40,0:56:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened the doors of tomorrow \Nand our future
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.47,0:56:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to make a promise that outlives time,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.50,0:56:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing every season yet to come \Nand piercing eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.34,0:57:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When we finally reach our destination \Nafter this long journey
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.00,0:57:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll look back and smile at the love \Nwe nurtured along the way
